{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":739,"text":"Where do you come from?"},{"time":2607,"text":"It's such a simple question,"},{"time":4678,"text":"but these days, of course,\nsimple questions"},{"time":6861,"text":"bring ever more complicated answers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":9907,"text":"People are always asking\nme where I come from,"},{"time":12859,"text":"and they're expecting me to say India,"},{"time":16039,"text":"and they're absolutely right\ninsofar as 100 percent"},{"time":19140,"text":"of my blood and ancestry\ndoes come from India."},{"time":22706,"text":"Except, I've never lived\none day of my life there."},{"time":26771,"text":"I can't speak even one word"},{"time":29179,"text":"of its more than 22,000 dialects."},{"time":32179,"text":"So I don't think I've really\nearned the right"},{"time":34389,"text":"to call myself an Indian."},{"time":36835,"text":"And if \"Where do you come from?\""},{"time":38383,"text":"means \"Where were you born\nand raised and educated?\""},{"time":41450,"text":"then I'm entirely\nof that funny little country"},{"time":43876,"text":"known as England,"},{"time":45247,"text":"except I left England\nas soon as I completed"},{"time":47658,"text":"my undergraduate education,"},{"time":49571,"text":"and all the time I was growing up,"},{"time":51288,"text":"I was the only kid in all my classes"},{"time":54084,"text":"who didn't begin to look\nlike the classic English heroes"},{"time":57213,"text":"represented in our textbooks."},{"time":59891,"text":"And if \"Where do you come from?\""},{"time":61193,"text":"means \"Where do you pay your taxes?"},{"time":62884,"text":"Where do you see your doctor\nand your dentist?\""},{"time":65432,"text":"then I'm very much of the United States,"},{"time":67795,"text":"and I have been for 48 years now,"},{"time":70363,"text":"since I was a really small child."},{"time":72451,"text":"Except, for many of those years,"},{"time":74159,"text":"I've had to carry around this\nfunny little pink card"},{"time":76660,"text":"with green lines running through my face"},{"time":78589,"text":"identifying me as a permanent alien."},{"time":81202,"text":"I do actually feel more alien\nthe longer I live there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":85464,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":87651,"text":"And if \"Where do you come from?\""},{"time":89238,"text":"means \"Which place goes deepest inside you"},{"time":92004,"text":"and where do you try\nto spend most of your time?\""},{"time":95184,"text":"then I'm Japanese,"},{"time":96357,"text":"because I've been living as much as I can"},{"time":98610,"text":"for the last 25 years in Japan."},{"time":101995,"text":"Except, all of those years\nI've been there on a tourist visa,"},{"time":105048,"text":"and I'm fairly sure not many Japanese"},{"time":107190,"text":"would want to consider me one of them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":110081,"text":"And I say all this just to stress"},{"time":113332,"text":"how very old-fashioned and straightforward"},{"time":116052,"text":"my background is,"},{"time":117051,"text":"because when I go to Hong\nKong or Sydney or Vancouver,"},{"time":121099,"text":"most of the kids I meet"},{"time":122995,"text":"are much more international\nand multi-cultured than I am."},{"time":126794,"text":"And they have one home\nassociated with their parents,"},{"time":129459,"text":"but another associated\nwith their partners,"},{"time":132615,"text":"a third connected maybe with the place\nwhere they happen to be,"},{"time":136004,"text":"a fourth connected with the place\nthey dream of being,"},{"time":138918,"text":"and many more besides."},{"time":141262,"text":"And their whole life will be\nspent taking pieces"},{"time":144548,"text":"of many different places\nand putting them together"},{"time":148035,"text":"into a stained glass whole."},{"time":150877,"text":"Home for them is really\na work in progress."},{"time":153318,"text":"It's like a project\non which they're constantly adding"},{"time":155914,"text":"upgrades and improvements and corrections."},{"time":159048,"text":"And for more and more of us,"},{"time":160943,"text":"home has really less to do\nwith a piece of soil"},{"time":165398,"text":"than, you could say, with a piece of soul."}]},{"cues":[{"time":168149,"text":"If somebody suddenly asks\nme, \"Where's your home?\""},{"time":170554,"text":"I think about my sweetheart\nor my closest friends"},{"time":173469,"text":"or the songs that travel with me\nwherever I happen to be."},{"time":177736,"text":"And I'd always felt this way,"},{"time":179593,"text":"but it really came home to me, as it were,"},{"time":182336,"text":"some years ago when\nI was climbing up the stairs"},{"time":185054,"text":"in my parents' house in California,"},{"time":187756,"text":"and I looked through the living\nroom windows"},{"time":190582,"text":"and I saw that we were\nencircled by 70-foot flames,"},{"time":195760,"text":"one of those wildfires\nthat regularly tear through"},{"time":198246,"text":"the hills of California\nand many other such places."},{"time":202077,"text":"And three hours later,\nthat fire had reduced"},{"time":205102,"text":"my home and every last thing in it"},{"time":207846,"text":"except for me to ash."},{"time":210864,"text":"And when I woke up the next morning,"},{"time":213574,"text":"I was sleeping on a friend's floor,"},{"time":215265,"text":"the only thing I had\nin the world was a toothbrush"},{"time":217693,"text":"I had just bought\nfrom an all-night supermarket."},{"time":220260,"text":"Of course, if anybody asked me then,"},{"time":222166,"text":"\"Where is your home?\""},{"time":223525,"text":"I literally couldn't point\nto any physical construction."},{"time":227517,"text":"My home would have to be whatever\nI carried around inside me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":232249,"text":"And in so many ways, I think\nthis is a terrific liberation."},{"time":236241,"text":"Because when my grandparents were born,"},{"time":238435,"text":"they pretty much had their sense of home,"},{"time":240962,"text":"their sense of community,\neven their sense of enmity,"},{"time":244454,"text":"assigned to them at birth,"},{"time":246379,"text":"and didn't have much chance\nof stepping outside of that."},{"time":249357,"text":"And nowadays, at least some of us\ncan choose our sense of home,"},{"time":253064,"text":"create our sense of community,"},{"time":255222,"text":"fashion our sense of self, and in so doing"},{"time":258803,"text":"maybe step a little beyond"},{"time":260940,"text":"some of the black and white divisions"},{"time":262726,"text":"of our grandparents' age."},{"time":264558,"text":"No coincidence that the president"},{"time":266442,"text":"of the strongest nation\non Earth is half-Kenyan,"},{"time":269173,"text":"partly raised in Indonesia,"},{"time":270780,"text":"has a Chinese-Canadian brother-in-law."}]},{"cues":[{"time":274379,"text":"The number of people living\nin countries not their own"},{"time":277843,"text":"now comes to 220 million,"},{"time":282630,"text":"and that's an almost unimaginable number,"},{"time":285244,"text":"but it means that if you took\nthe whole population of Canada"},{"time":288994,"text":"and the whole population of Australia"},{"time":290910,"text":"and then the whole population\nof Australia again"},{"time":293220,"text":"and the whole population of Canada again"},{"time":295862,"text":"and doubled that number,"},{"time":297545,"text":"you would still have\nfewer people than belong"},{"time":299712,"text":"to this great floating tribe."}]},{"cues":[{"time":301919,"text":"And the number of us who live outside"},{"time":303705,"text":"the old nation-state categories\nis increasing so quickly,"},{"time":307789,"text":"by 64 million just in the last 12 years,"},{"time":311419,"text":"that soon there will be more\nof us than there are Americans."},{"time":314899,"text":"Already, we represent\nthe fifth-largest nation on Earth."},{"time":319573,"text":"And in fact, in Canada's largest\ncity, Toronto,"},{"time":322429,"text":"the average resident today\nis what used to be called"},{"time":326119,"text":"a foreigner, somebody born\nin a very different country."}]},{"cues":[{"time":330211,"text":"And I've always felt that the beauty\nof being surrounded by the foreign"},{"time":334000,"text":"is that it slaps you awake."},{"time":335597,"text":"You can't take anything for granted."},{"time":338401,"text":"Travel, for me, is a little bit\nlike being in love,"},{"time":341135,"text":"because suddenly all your senses\nare at the setting marked \"on.\""},{"time":345192,"text":"Suddenly you're alert to the secret\npatterns of the world."},{"time":349193,"text":"The real voyage of discovery,\nas Marcel Proust famously said,"},{"time":353509,"text":"consists not in seeing new sights,"},{"time":356507,"text":"but in looking with new eyes."},{"time":358877,"text":"And of course, once you have new eyes,"},{"time":360843,"text":"even the old sights, even your home"},{"time":363280,"text":"become something different."},{"time":365957,"text":"Many of the people living\nin countries not their own"},{"time":368775,"text":"are refugees who never\nwanted to leave home"},{"time":371858,"text":"and ache to go back home."},{"time":374574,"text":"But for the fortunate among us,"},{"time":376221,"text":"I think the age of movement brings\nexhilarating new possibilities."}]},{"cues":[{"time":380502,"text":"Certainly when I'm traveling,"},{"time":381567,"text":"especially to the major\ncities of the world,"},{"time":383881,"text":"the typical person I meet today"},{"time":386006,"text":"will be, let's say, a half-Korean,\nhalf-German young woman"},{"time":390551,"text":"living in Paris."},{"time":392254,"text":"And as soon as she meets a half-Thai,"},{"time":395312,"text":"half-Canadian young guy from Edinburgh,"},{"time":398526,"text":"she recognizes him as kin."},{"time":401003,"text":"She realizes that she probably\nhas much more in common with him"},{"time":405342,"text":"than with anybody entirely\nof Korea or entirely of Germany."},{"time":408935,"text":"So they become friends. They fall in love."},{"time":411693,"text":"They move to New York City."}]},{"cues":[{"time":413971,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":416134,"text":"Or Edinburgh."},{"time":417520,"text":"And the little girl\nwho arises out of their union"},{"time":420794,"text":"will of course be not Korean or German"},{"time":422925,"text":"or French or Thai or Scotch or Canadian"},{"time":425468,"text":"or even American, but a wonderful"},{"time":427573,"text":"and constantly evolving\nmix of all those places."},{"time":431707,"text":"And potentially, everything about the way"},{"time":434472,"text":"that young woman dreams about the world,"},{"time":437221,"text":"writes about the world,\nthinks about the world,"},{"time":440267,"text":"could be something different,"},{"time":442237,"text":"because it comes out of this\nalmost unprecedented"},{"time":445432,"text":"blend of cultures."}]},{"cues":[{"time":447405,"text":"Where you come from now\nis much less important"},{"time":450489,"text":"than where you're going."},{"time":452137,"text":"More and more of us\nare rooted in the future"},{"time":454533,"text":"or the present tense\nas much as in the past."},{"time":457829,"text":"And home, we know, is not just the place"},{"time":460392,"text":"where you happen to be born."},{"time":462502,"text":"It's the place where you become yourself."}]},{"cues":[{"time":466975,"text":"And yet,"},{"time":469397,"text":"there is one great problem with movement,"},{"time":472062,"text":"and that is that it's really\nhard to get your bearings"},{"time":475273,"text":"when you're in midair."},{"time":476891,"text":"Some years ago, I noticed\nthat I had accumulated"},{"time":480177,"text":"one million miles\non United Airlines alone."},{"time":483699,"text":"You all know that crazy system,"},{"time":485749,"text":"six days in hell, you get\nthe seventh day free."}]},{"cues":[{"time":489477,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":492983,"text":"And I began to think that really,"},{"time":495259,"text":"movement was only as good\nas the sense of stillness"},{"time":498538,"text":"that you could bring to it\nto put it into perspective."}]},{"cues":[{"time":502385,"text":"And eight months\nafter my house burned down,"},{"time":505239,"text":"I ran into a friend who taught\nat a local high school,"},{"time":507961,"text":"and he said, \"I've got\nthe perfect place for you.\""},{"time":511493,"text":"\"Really?\" I said. I'm\nalways a bit skeptical"},{"time":513501,"text":"when people say things like that."},{"time":514979,"text":"\"No, honestly,\" he went on,"},{"time":516349,"text":"\"it's only three hours away by car,"},{"time":518195,"text":"and it's not very expensive,"},{"time":519809,"text":"and it's probably not like anywhere\nyou've stayed before.\""},{"time":523389,"text":"\"Hmm.\" I was beginning to get\nslightly intrigued. \"What is it?\""},{"time":527588,"text":"\"Well —\" Here my friend hemmed and hawed —"},{"time":530367,"text":"\"Well, actually\nit's a Catholic hermitage.\""},{"time":533949,"text":"This was the wrong answer."},{"time":535915,"text":"I had spent 15 years in Anglican schools,"},{"time":538462,"text":"so I had had enough hymnals\nand crosses to last me a lifetime."},{"time":543060,"text":"Several lifetimes, actually."},{"time":545331,"text":"But my friend assured me\nthat he wasn't Catholic,"},{"time":547889,"text":"nor were most of his students,"},{"time":549342,"text":"but he took his classes\nthere every spring."},{"time":552123,"text":"And as he had it,\neven the most restless, distractible,"},{"time":556886,"text":"testosterone-addled\n15-year-old Californian boy"},{"time":560920,"text":"only had to spend three days in silence"},{"time":564156,"text":"and something in him cooled\ndown and cleared out."},{"time":568410,"text":"He found himself."},{"time":570719,"text":"And I thought, \"Anything\nthat works for a 15-year-old boy"},{"time":573458,"text":"ought to work for me.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":574797,"text":"So I got in my car,\nand I drove three hours north"},{"time":578407,"text":"along the coast,"},{"time":579883,"text":"and the roads grew emptier and narrower,"},{"time":582443,"text":"and then I turned\nonto an even narrower path,"},{"time":585207,"text":"barely paved, that snaked for two miles"},{"time":588847,"text":"up to the top of a mountain."},{"time":591370,"text":"And when I got out of my car,"},{"time":594209,"text":"the air was pulsing."},{"time":596579,"text":"The whole place was absolutely silent,"},{"time":598439,"text":"but the silence wasn't\nan absence of noise."},{"time":601899,"text":"It was really a presence of a kind\nof energy or quickening."},{"time":605940,"text":"And at my feet was the great,\nstill blue plate"},{"time":609451,"text":"of the Pacific Ocean."},{"time":611705,"text":"All around me were 800\nacres of wild dry brush."}]},{"cues":[{"time":616139,"text":"And I went down to the room\nin which I was to be sleeping."},{"time":618925,"text":"Small but eminently comfortable,"},{"time":620650,"text":"it had a bed and a rocking chair"},{"time":622859,"text":"and a long desk and even longer\npicture windows"},{"time":626033,"text":"looking out on a small,\nprivate, walled garden,"},{"time":630322,"text":"and then 1,200 feet of golden pampas grass"},{"time":633522,"text":"running down to the sea."},{"time":636514,"text":"And I sat down, and I began to write,"},{"time":639683,"text":"and write, and write,"},{"time":641187,"text":"even though I'd gone there\nreally to get away from my desk."},{"time":644800,"text":"And by the time I got up,\nfour hours had passed."},{"time":649294,"text":"Night had fallen,"},{"time":651423,"text":"and I went out under this great\noverturned saltshaker of stars,"},{"time":656179,"text":"and I could see the tail lights of cars"},{"time":658431,"text":"disappearing around the headlands\n12 miles to the south."},{"time":662644,"text":"And it really seemed\nlike my concerns of the previous day"},{"time":666352,"text":"vanishing."},{"time":668302,"text":"And the next day, when I woke up"},{"time":670114,"text":"in the absence of telephones\nand TVs and laptops,"},{"time":673582,"text":"the days seemed to stretch\nfor a thousand hours."},{"time":677735,"text":"It was really all the freedom\nI know when I'm traveling,"},{"time":681434,"text":"but it also profoundly\nfelt like coming home."},{"time":686048,"text":"And I'm not a religious person,"},{"time":687664,"text":"so I didn't go to the services."},{"time":689165,"text":"I didn't consult the monks for guidance."},{"time":691734,"text":"I just took walks along the monastery road"},{"time":694514,"text":"and sent postcards to loved ones."},{"time":696863,"text":"I looked at the clouds,"},{"time":698697,"text":"and I did what is hardest\nof all for me to do usually,"},{"time":703022,"text":"which is nothing at all."}]},{"cues":[{"time":705516,"text":"And I started to go back to this place,"},{"time":707824,"text":"and I noticed that I was doing\nmy most important work there"},{"time":711392,"text":"invisibly just by sitting still,"},{"time":714923,"text":"and certainly coming\nto my most critical decisions"},{"time":718048,"text":"the way I never could when I was racing"},{"time":720330,"text":"from the last email\nto the next appointment."},{"time":722903,"text":"And I began to think that something in me"},{"time":725532,"text":"had really been crying out for stillness,"},{"time":727521,"text":"but of course I couldn't hear it"},{"time":729069,"text":"because I was running around so much."},{"time":730855,"text":"I was like some crazy guy\nwho puts on a blindfold"},{"time":733508,"text":"and then complains\nthat he can't see a thing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":736739,"text":"And I thought back\nto that wonderful phrase"},{"time":739280,"text":"I had learned as a boy from Seneca,"},{"time":741652,"text":"in which he says, \"That man is poor"},{"time":745310,"text":"not who has little but who hankers\nafter more.\""},{"time":750683,"text":"And, of course, I'm not suggesting"},{"time":752775,"text":"that anybody here go into a monastery."},{"time":754609,"text":"That's not the point."},{"time":756201,"text":"But I do think\nit's only by stopping movement"},{"time":759919,"text":"that you can see where to go."},{"time":762215,"text":"And it's only by stepping\nout of your life and the world"},{"time":765820,"text":"that you can see what you\nmost deeply care about"},{"time":769389,"text":"and find a home."}]},{"cues":[{"time":771795,"text":"And I've noticed so many people now"},{"time":773838,"text":"take conscious measures\nto sit quietly for 30 minutes"},{"time":776926,"text":"every morning just collecting themselves"},{"time":779459,"text":"in one corner of the room\nwithout their devices,"},{"time":782019,"text":"or go running every evening,"},{"time":784092,"text":"or leave their cell phones behind"},{"time":786048,"text":"when they go to have a long\nconversation with a friend."},{"time":789965,"text":"Movement is a fantastic privilege,"},{"time":793134,"text":"and it allows us to do so\nmuch that our grandparents"},{"time":796491,"text":"could never have dreamed of doing."},{"time":798612,"text":"But movement, ultimately,"},{"time":800517,"text":"only has a meaning if you\nhave a home to go back to."}]},{"cues":[{"time":805058,"text":"And home, in the end, is of course"},{"time":807849,"text":"not just the place where you sleep."},{"time":810717,"text":"It's the place where you stand."}]},{"cues":[{"time":813356,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":814813,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}